## 2.3 How StudyVault Improves Upon Existing Systems

StudyVault combines the simplicity of a file-sharing tool with the structured workflow of an LMS, while adding an AI-powered safety layer not present in any of the reviewed systems. Key improvements are:

1. **Automated AI Pre-Screening:** Every note is scanned using an AI model before faculty see it, which reduces manual effort and ensures only safe content reaches the review stage.
2. **Complete Notes Lifecycle Management:** The system tracks each note from upload through AI analysis, faculty decision, and final publication — no other reviewed system does this end-to-end.
3. **Faculty-Subject Binding:** Faculty members only see notes in subjects they are assigned to, which mirrors the real-world academic workflow.
